      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS, delivering linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock for optimal mechanical grip. This specimen is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement and has undergone proactive rod bearing replacement. The factory finish is preserved with exceptional depth, and the suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing original spec bushings and dampers. A truly concours-ready driver's car with full service provenance.",
